reviewText:
Excellent dvd set
Arrived super fast
The best gangster movie out there!
Just as I had remembered it... Great and Fantastic!!

A classic gangster movie is always a winner.  A previously owned disk that works as advertised is a jewel.  I try to find movies that are new, but it's not always possible when you wait twenty years or more to purchase it.  In this case, waiting was to my advantage.
A total 5 Star gem. Well worth the 4 plus hours it takes to view it. Ready to watch it again. Great story, performances, atmosphere and score.
I got the movie as a present for my husband on Father's Day she was thrilled.
One of favorite movies. My cousin James Hayden was in this movie. He played Patsy, Patrick Goldberg. ONe of the main characters.
